      "education": "MCS Analytics for Business, Data analysis & IA\nEugenia School\n10/2023 \u0000 01/2025  Paris\nLearned Python programming for data analysis & automation\nBuilt interactive dashboards with Power BI\nApplied Machine Learning models (classification, forecasting)\nWorked with APIs and workflow automation tools\nBachelor in Business Development & Marketing\nEM Normandie Business School\n09/2022 \u0000 08/2023  Paris\nLearned marketing strategy and consumer behavior to support \nbusiness growth.",
      "certifications": "Python for Machine Learning\nLinkedIn\nFine-Tuning for LLMs\nLinkedIn\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\nE  q \n?\ng\na\nB",
      "skills": "management \u0000CRM\u0000.\nLANGUAGES\nFrench\nNative\nEnglish\nBusiness\nRESUME\nand marketing, turning data and insights into \nactionable solutions to improve efficiency, \ncommunication, and decision-making.\nREALISATION\nEnhanced conversion efficiency\nImproved customer conversion rates by \n10% with optimized CRM pipelines.\nBuilt Interactive Dashboards\nDeveloped dashboards increasing sales \ntracking accuracy by 20%.\nImplemented predictive models\nSuccessfully forecasted demand, \nimproving opportunity tracking by 25%.\nCreated marketing content & event \nmaterials\nDesigned and produced content for \nemail campaign"
